  "body": "Starting from version `2.3.0b20250611`, the llama-cpp-ipex-llm **Xeon** portable zip supports AMX and TP.\r\nStarting from version `2.3.0b20250724`, the llama-cpp-ipex-llm portable zip supports llama-mtmd-cli/llama-mtmd-cli.exe for running Multimodal models.\r\n\r\nStarting from version `2.3.0b20250630`, the ollama-ipex-llm portable zip supports ollama v0.9.3 .\r\n\r\n> ⚠️ **Warning**  \r\n> Model loading with `mmap` can potentially leak data via side-channels in multi-tenant or shared-host environments.  \r\n> Our package is intended for personal use on individual machines only, and is not recommended in multi-tenant/shared-host scenarios.  \r\n> If such an environment is required, please explicitly disable mmap by adding the option:  \r\n> ```bash\r\n> --no-mmap\r\n> ```",
